snippet.title: Battlewake - E3 2019 Announcement Trailer | PS VR
snippet.description:
Avast, matey! Battlewake is landing on PS VR summer 2019.

Set sail in Battlewake as four ancient, super-powered Pirate Lords fighting for ultimate dominion! You’ll captain a massive battle-ready ship; navigate lush, elemental seascapes; and embark on a larger-than-life nautical war for the ages.
